			<td class="BoardRowB" colspan=2 width="83%">
				It has become clearly aparant that the population of the server is hurting and the reason this is, is because the lack of ways to contact and make a viable group. Anon has nothing to do with rpin. This game was made to group interact and make it easy to meet other people and share adventure and fun together. I have talked too about 100 people and they all state that the way too make this server alive again and a better server is too remove Anon so grouping can become easier. So state here if you believe Anon should be removed and maybe verant/sony will look at this and see how the people feel. Don;t you hate when you message one of the 10 people lfg worldwide on FV and they tell you there 15 levels out of your league? <br>  <br> Be Well		

