			<td class="BoardRowB" colspan=2 width="83%">
				This once i agree with Lasgalen(though it is rare)...if it was that simple then a piece of the role-playing aspects would be lost...I am happy with this rule, even though it has made everything more difficult. We are forced to learn other race's languages. We are forced  to not group with the opposite alignment(good, evil). We are forced to complete quests at appropriate levels(trivial loot code). And i believe all of this enhances the Firiona Vie Experience. I wont call u whiny...but all this encourages role-play which is the point of this server. I sincerely hope that u dont leave due to a simple thing as this, for i think I've met ur character and was delighted to be in their presence. <br>  <br> Xelissen		

